{"tid":1517892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Black Bloc及防具整合 (附購買地點)","createTime":"2019-08-30T05:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T12:29:18.000Z","uid":61886,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d481216c3dab5707a88092fde60177352e4bf87c","tid":1517892,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:13:28.000Z","msg":"一兩個月前我開過幾個關於裝備既post<br />\n見最近有不少新血加入野餐<br />\n所以我再整理一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下裝備分為 &quot;<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">隱藏身份</span></span>&quot; 及 &quot;<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">防具</span></span>&quot; <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一. 隱藏身份的重要性</span></strong><br />\n首先我地參考一下魚蛋果時既相片<br />\n我地睇到好多義士都係得一個口罩<br />\n因為魚蛋果時係試過用頭髮 耳仔 墨 等等去檢控<br />\n個人特徵一定要遮<br />\neg. 紋身、大既耳窿等等<br />\n到最終好多義士被拘捕 搜證 最終入獄<br />\n魚革係好沉重既事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HHxxUar.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHHxxUar.jpg&h=5c271563&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n義士魚蛋燒的士時除口罩最終被入罪<br />\n<br />\n我地更加要汲取教訓<br />\n就係如何好好隱藏身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳細可閱<br />\n[歷史的意義] 魚蛋革命拘捕及判刑時間線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1286684\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1286684</a><br />\n<br />\n你地咁撚樣戴口罩 第時實比人秋後算帳<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1513436\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1513436</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>二. 前線先需要隱藏身份？</strong></span><br />\n見到大家去野餐果時<br />\n好多人口罩都唔戴<br />\n心態上覺得 我都係喺後排行下坐下<br />\n唔驚會拉我啦<br />\n其實咁諗你都岩 但只岩左一半<br />\n<br />\n因為當前線同後排都著到好相似<br />\n亦都遮掩晒可以比人認出既特徵<br />\n無論係義士定大家都好<br />\n都會大大加強搜證既難度<br />\n義士被入罪機會亦大大減低<br />\n<br />\n而家仲要有監控燈柱<br />\n其實剩戴一個口罩<br />\n係同無戴無分別<br />\n<br />\n再加上而家政府玩白色恐佈<br />\n難保和理非都會被清算<br />\n<br />\n但重點係 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">當場被捕 著到ironman咁都無用<br />\n所以Black Bloc要配合不被捕<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">三. Black Bloc示範</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fua0iDa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffua0iDa.jpg&h=af2a093f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OrhxUa4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOrhxUa4.jpg&h=e726123c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBlack Bloc Do &amp; Don't<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X2OARXO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX2OARXO.jpg&h=f72eb2e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我都好怕熱 但更怕坐監</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"1d1e40378e1cdbc36b627eb005297a8ec8b6a457","tid":1517892,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:13:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhik2fq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhik2fq.gif&h=7b54c7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8kVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=0c05cf02\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8kVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=65059aae\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8kVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=9205776b\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"f364288a2d06f7ef0f9378ea6cc1c371995a7a7c","tid":1517892,"uid":61886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:14:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">四. &quot;隱藏身份&quot; 裝備</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<ins>口罩</ins><br />\n唔介紹啦 大家都識買<br />\n購買地點：邊度都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>面罩/頭巾</ins><br />\n好處係可以包圍耳仔同兩邊面頰<br />\n但要小心太薄 比人影相再PS係可以出返個樣出黎 所以先口罩再頭巾也可考慮<br />\n<br />\n購買地點：Dacathlon $19 (得某啲色) / 深水埗電子特賣城 $5 (之前睇有 而家唔知)<br />\n<br />\nPS黑衫包頭都可以 但記得要搵件透氣既衫<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kAL30RN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkAL30RN.jpg&h=7ae1a449&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>Cap帽</ins><br />\n髮型係好易認 尤其你髮型或髮色較特別<br />\n女仔記得扎頭髮<br />\n購買地點：H&amp;M $49 <br />\n<br />\n<ins>太陽眼鏡</ins><br />\n遮眼係必需 唔遮眼好易認出<br />\n購買地點：Aeon $12店 $12 (有專門再<br />\n比戴眼鏡既人戴既黑超)"},{"pid":"a5425de31b4aee19af25319a4b70e6cb4f8cba0c","tid":1517892,"uid":61886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:14:20.000Z","msg":"<ins>冰袖</ins><br />\n如果你手有紋身或明顯特徵<br />\n就一定要遮<br />\n購買地點：深水埗電子特賣城 $9<br />\n<br />\n<ins>背囊 (加背囊套)</ins><br />\n唔好用明顯鮮色既背囊<br />\n唔好喺背囊掛公仔<br />\n最好既可以用前線御用背囊 Dacathlon $79<br />\n無論用咩背囊都好 都要加背囊套<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">畜龍捉人一定係扯袋<br />\n多個套 等如多條命</span></strong></span><br />\n購買地點：深水埗電子特賣城 ($10)<br />\n<br />\n<ins>腰包</ins><br />\n重要物件放腰包<br />\nworst case棄背囊<br />\n購買地點：Dacathlon ($39)<br />\n<br />\n<ins>褲</ins><br />\n長褲 不解釋了<br />\n<br />\n<ins>鞋</ins><br />\n唔好著貴鞋或者鮮色鞋<br />\n見過有人著offwhite yeezy出去"},{"pid":"d77225946115b8671bba30af08b313bf7e52b553","tid":1517892,"uid":61886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:14:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五. 防具裝備</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<ins>手套</ins><br />\n無論做咩都好 戴手套<br />\n衰極都勞工手套<br />\n好少少既3m防刮手套<br />\n購買地點：五金舖 (3m防刮手套 $32)<br />\n<br />\n<ins>頭盔</ins><br />\n最普通既係黃或白色地盤安全帽 ($45)<br />\n較強既係電單車頭盔<br />\n自己衡量要邊款<br />\n<br />\n<ins>眼罩 (泳鏡)</ins><br />\n如果目的係防煙 要揀啲眼罩係貼晒面既<br />\n但唔易搵到 所以用泳鏡會更好 <br />\n個人建議<br />\n泳鏡 (近視巴打配近視泳鏡) + 防彈眼罩 + 反光貼<br />\n<br />\n反光貼可睇返我之前個post<br />\n[721 - 裝備] 眼罩都係時候要進化！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1327634\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1327634</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>豬咀</ins><br />\n不解釋了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4KqPbY0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4KqPbY0.png&h=896239c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>行山枚</ins><br />\n主要用於對暴徒藍絲同黑社會<br />\n購買地點：Dacathlon $57<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">裝備好自己 不被捕 不受傷<br />\n齊上齊落<br />\n武運享通<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"36a549c066d7d18e68a7b9f15c110f08d83f80af","tid":1517892,"uid":61886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k4HaFVa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk4HaFVa.jpg&h=7803e06d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af55174a7488b92c7fb29d46baa0c5b21537c126","tid":1517892,"uid":7738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:17:15.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">:)</code></pre>"},{"pid":"e63ea4a83fd6d621c4c3e99ab28c184e05366330","tid":1517892,"uid":43657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:19:13.000Z","msg":"要包到阿媽都認唔到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66332914d8f28c3955c5f51b3341cde0bd7042bd","tid":1517892,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:19:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c016YHJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc016YHJ.png&h=08a3d297&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ed8f88c13cd1065ce3a59eb3c05398a9c2e6661","tid":1517892,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:22:11.000Z","msg":"[必睇][香城攻略]星期日除左入機場涼冷氣即興去旅行，仲可以遊山玩水！！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1517745\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1517745</a>"},{"pid":"a5382d1d79b3ae3892e1c33ebce98b8948dc97ee","tid":1517892,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0049476d36e37d9be63fcfce70301493affb6a88","tid":1517892,"uid":121855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:32:24.000Z","msg":"我一包面巾塊面就痕到死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d1a9116745372837eb40809a3f45c59c369ddb","tid":1517892,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}